    private class CrimeListLoadingFragment.CrimeListLoadingAsyncTaskHandler
extends CrimeDataLoadingFragment.CrimeDataLoadingAsyncTaskHandler
    CrimeListLoadingAsyncTaskHandler is a helper class used to wrap the crime list data loading task for this fragment.

    This class is a specialized CrimeDataLoadingFragment.CrimeDataLoadingAsyncTaskHandler for wrapping a GetCrimeListAsyncTask.
